## Monitoring

### Health Checks

```yaml
# config/deploy.yml

healthcheck:
  path: /up
  port: 3000
  interval: 10s
  timeout: 5s
  max_attempts: 7
```

```ruby
# config/routes.rb

get '/up', to: 'rails/health#show', as: :rails_health_check
```

### Logs

```bash
# Application logs
kamal app logs --follow

# Last 100 lines
kamal app logs --tail 100

# Since specific time
kamal app logs --since 1h

# Filter by string
kamal app logs | grep ERROR
```

